  </div>
  <div class="col-md-7">
    <h2 class="featurette-heading">What is Dragon Boat?</h2>
    <p class="lead">A dragon boat is a human powered boat (Paddled Water Craft) traditionally made of teak wood (in modern day the sport has seen the surge of boats made with fiberglass propelled by high tech carbon fiber paddles) in various designs and sizes. It is one of a family of Traditional Long Boats found throughout Asia, Africa and the Pacific Islands. The boat is used in dragon boat racing which originated in China over 2000 years ago.</p>
  </div>
</div>

