<div class="row featurette" id="dragonboating-worldwide">
  <div class="col-md-7">
    <h2 class="featurette-heading">Dragon boating worldwide.</h2>
    <p class="lead">Today, dragon boat is one of the world's fastest growing water sports. It is currently the second most popular team sport in the world; only soccer surpasses it. There are nearly 50 million people who currently take part annually in dragon boat races worldwide. Dragon boat races are held in countries all around the world. The majority of the racers are in China and the Far East. It is estimated that over 150,000 participants are in Europe, 50,000 in North America, and 20,000 in Australia.</p>
  </div>
